        "description": "You too can join this noble initiative of building a greener world by planting trees. A single sapling can become a breath of fresh air for future generations.",
        "content": "<h3>Program Details</h3><p class='editor-paragraph editor-empty'></p><div data-youtube-video=\"\"><iframe class=\"editor-youtube-video\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" autoplay=\"false\" disablekbcontrols=\"false\" enableiframeapi=\"false\" endtime=\"0\" ivloadpolicy=\"0\" loop=\"false\" modestbranding=\"true\" origin=\"\" playlist=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/099lbWQGq0g\" start=\"0\"></iframe></div><p class=\"editor-paragraph editor-empty\"></p><p class='editor-paragraph'>One of the main reasons for the global rise in temperature and environmental imbalance is deforestation. The number of trees is decreasing day by day. To combat climate change and global warming and protect human civilization, the noble Sunnah of the Prophet Muhammad (PBUH) — tree plantation — is essential. Recognizing this need and as a part of Sadaqah Jariyah, As-Sunnah Foundation has launched a nationwide tree plantation campaign.</p>",
